## üåê Project Overview

This is a static HTML/CSS website created to showcase Tee Networks‚Äô services and promote user engagement. The website is ideal for academic, personal, or demonstration purposes and features key sections such as:

- Company branding/logo
- Navigation menu
- About Us
- Services overview
- Testimonials
- Contact information
- Social media links

